      <li>URL from Atlanta (33.917, -84.3378) to Bald Mountain to Grassy Mtn: http://goo.gl/maps/LNlI3</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Seasonal/Limited Access</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>March 1 - December 31 (per http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/conf/recreation/hiking/recarea/?recid=10465&amp;actid=104), and there are gates.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Directions to Bald Mtn Trailhead</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>[See driving directions in my <a href="http://k4kpk.com/content/sota-guide-w4ghc-007-grassy-mountain">Grassy Mtn</a> guide.  The drive to Bald Mtn is 95% of the drive to Grassy Mtn.]</li>
